<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="out-adv-prep">out <strong><em>adv &amp; prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /aʊt/    美 /aʊt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>出外；在外；向外：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let’s eat out tonight.
我们今晚出去吃吧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Is Mr Smith in?
史密斯先生在家吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— No, he is out.
不，他出去了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>尽；完：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The fire is out.
火灭了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The tickets for the concert are all <strong>sold out</strong>.
音乐会的门票已全部售完。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>出现；盛开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The stars are out.
星星出来了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The flowers are out.
花开了。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>大声地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Speak out!
大声说！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="out-of">out of</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>从...中 (出去)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She went <strong>out of the room</strong>.
她走出了房间。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Six out of ten people worldwide use mobile phones.
全世界10个人中就有6个使用手机。</p></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>在... (范围) 之外；脱离 (某状态)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>out of control
失控</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The plane is <strong>out of sight</strong> now.
飞机已飞出了视线。</p></div>

<p>3.<strong>出于；由于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>out of concern for one’s friend
出于对朋友的关心</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I ran away <strong>out of fear</strong> of the dog.
我怕狗，于是跑开了。</p></div>

<p>4.★ <strong>缺乏；没有：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>out of work</strong>
失业</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am feeling completely <strong>out of practice</strong>.
我感觉自己太疏于练习了。</p><footer>2008 广东</footer></div>

<p>5.★ <strong>凭借；用… (制成)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make</strong> a box <strong>out of</strong> wood
用木头做个盒子</p></div></div>